2006-06-03	<carlosc@uvic.ca>

	* marsyas-swig/ruby : Added comment to *.i & *.rb files. Version (0.3.5)

	* configure.ac : Fixed ruby install variables to use prefix.

2006-06-02	<carlosc@uvic.ca>
	
	* marsyas-swig (update): Added documentation for package. Version (0.3.4)
	
	* marsyas-swig : Version (0.3.3)

	* marsyas-swig/ruby : Moved Ruby specific code to ruby subdir.

	* marsyas-swig/common : Moved common marsyas.i to common subdir.

	* marsyas-swig : Version (0.3.1)
	
	* marsyas-swig/python : Made python version & subdir.

2006-06-01	<carlosc@uvic.ca>
	
	* marsyas-swig : Using autoconf/automake/libtool instead of trying to get mkmf
	to work properly, and now can be build / installed with marsyas. Version (0.2.1)

	* marsyas : Patched configure.in to allow for marsyas-swig as a
	subfolder (swig) to be configured, built and installed as part of
	marsyas.

2006-05-30	<carlosc@uvic.ca>
	
	* marsyas-swig (update) : Completed special Ruby wrapper for *special* features
	like automatic class & property generation. Bump version to (0.1.1).

	* marsyas-swig : Initial version (0.0.1). Supports similar interface
	to older pysyas, but written for Ruby. Uses Ruby's mkmf, but shouldn't
	be installed.
